metadata.title: Early Life History Literature Database

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Marine Fisheries Service (NMFS), Alaska Fisheries Science Center (AFSC)

metadata.description: A Procite bibliographic reference database that features publications referencing fish mostly in the northeast Pacific Ocean, the Bering Sea, and the Atlantic Ocean.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: This database was created to assist the local lab users as a desktop reference. The database can be packaged in a CD and made available to non-local lab users.
